KeysToEntries.story_4_2_000:
Got a clear picture
of your ability.
KeysToEntries.story_4_2_001:
Pisses me off…
you give off the same vibe
as that idiot…
KeysToEntries.story_4_2_002:
The one who beat me…
Akina’s 86…!!
KeysToEntries.story_4_2_003:
But even so…
you’re still no match for me…!!
KeysToEntries.story_4_2_004:
If you want to challenge my brother,
then you’ll have to
beat me first!
KeysToEntries.story_4_2_005:
Here we go!
Time to show you
some real effort…!!
